=============================
Editplus Color Schema for VIM
=============================

EditPlus : A color scheme that mimics the standard scheme found in the EditPlus text editor.

It's customized light gray color schema. The original schema is here-
http://vim.sourceforge.net/scripts/script.php?script_id=4087

How to install
==============

Just put it in "~/.vim/colors" or in "<your vim directory>\vimfiles\colors" on Windows.

Do ":color editplus" to apply it. If you want to install it as your default color scheme, just add "color editplus" to your vimrc file.
